headline.main: East Libyan Forces Mobilising for Counter Attack at Oil Ports - Officials
headline.print_headline: East Libyan Forces Mobilising for Counter Attack at Oil Ports - Officials

lead_paragraph: East Libyan forces carried out fresh air strikes on Monday and said they were mobilising ground forces as they attempt to win back two of Libya's largest oil ports, military officials said.
